description:
Animal's Super Senses - Episode 7: Perfect Timing | Wildlife Documentary

Watch 'Animal's Super Senses - Episode 8' here: https://youtu.be/dT5s1xHAStw

In this episode, we examine how every animal has what could be called a sense of rhythm – the human animal included. To give an obvious example, our internal body clock responds to the so-called Circadian rhythm. That’s the 24-hour night and day cycle.
